Scallfolding facilitates in this folder is aimming to create a database enabled Java EE environment for SMU.

[Usage]
1. Change or replace your context.xml in <tomcat_root>/conf/ folder
2. Set your environment variable HSQLDB_HOME to your HSQLDB installation, e.g. /opt/hsqldb
3. Start/stop db by execute start.sh or stop.sh


[Windows Platform]
It should be similar with this solution for Linux, to be supported later.


